data.description:
USDA Approved! Well maintained and spacious family home in a very convenient location at Cross Oaks Ranch. Huge master bedroom on 1st level and 3 spacious bedrooms are upstairs with a huge gameroom. The back patio has complete wiring and equipped with lights and 2 ceiling fans to keep you cool in the summer heat as you barbecue. This 2013 home feels like new.. 
This DR Horton home has high quality insulation and Radiant barrier that keep the utility bills very low.
All furniture are like new and are all negotiable. The alarm system and 3 Bluetooth  cameras (valued at $750)  program will be transferable to new owner for free if owner want to keep the popular Homepro alarm company.
